---

<Layout 
  title="Aiello Hotels Milano - Tariffa scontata del 10%"
  description="Aiello Hotels - Aiello Rooms - Aiello suites - Tariffa scontata del 10% rispetto a qualsiasi sito di prenotazione - Cancellazione gratuita - Nessuna penale. Soggiorna in tutta sicurezza."
  locale="it_IT"
>
  <div class="bg-hero w-full flex flex-col items-center gap-10 text-white text-center pt-10 pb-44 z-0">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-secondary uppercase">Aiello Hotels</h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-thin">Strategically located in Milan<br/>Welcoming Guests since 2014</p>
    <a href="https://pay.syshotelonline.it/reserva/sc_scheda.php?catena=8&hotel=97&lingua=I&stile=aiellosuite.css" target="_blank" class="bg-secondary text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-secondary transition-all duration-200 uppercase text-lg md:text-xl py-3 px-5 rounded-md flex flex-row items-center gap-2 group">
      Verifica Disponibilità
      <ChevronRight className="w-0 -translate-x-2 opacity-0 group-hover:translate-x-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:w-5 h-5 transition-all duration-200" />
    </a>
    <div class="pattern"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full bg-primary text-secondary text-center py-7">
    <p class="text-xl md:text-4xl">Scegli la struttura</p>
  </div>
  <GoogleMap client:load locations={locations} />
  <div class="mx-auto py-14 w-full max-w-screen-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10">
    <p class="text-primary text-2xl md:text-4xl text-center">Perchè prenotare direttamente?</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-y-8 justify-items-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 max-w-[250px] text-center">
        <div class="rounded-full bg-secondary p-3">
          <CircleDollarSign className="w-10 h-10 text-primary" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-primary text-lg">Migliore tariffa garantita</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-base">
          Tariffa scontata del 10% rispetto a qualsiasi tariffa sui siti di intermediazione
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 max-w-[250px] text-center">
        <div class="rounded-full bg-secondary p-3">
          <HandCoins className="w-10 h-10 text-primary" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-primary text-lg">Cancellazione gratuita</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-base">
          Cancellazione gratuita fino alla mezzanotte del giorno prima dell’arrivo
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 max-w-[250px] text-center">
        <div class="rounded-full bg-secondary p-3">
          <ShieldCheck className="w-10 h-10 text-primary" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-primary text-lg">Nessuna penale applicata, mai</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-base">
          Non riesci comunque a godere del soggiorno? <br/> Ti riserviamo un voucher da poter utilizzare per un soggiorno futuro
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 max-w-[250px] text-center">
        <div class="rounded-full bg-secondary p-3">
          <Pointer className="w-10 h-10 text-primary" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-primary text-lg">Online check-in</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-base">
          Risparmia tempo ed effettua check-in self service in tutta sicurezza
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 max-w-[250px] text-center">
        <div class="rounded-full bg-secondary p-3">
          <CalendarCheck className="w-10 h-10 text-primary" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-primary text-lg">Tariffe ed orari personalizzati</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-base">
          Personalizziamo le tariffe e gli orari in base alle tue necessità di day use o office use
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 max-w-[250px] text-center">
        <div class="rounded-full bg-secondary p-3">
          <Gift className="w-10 h-10 text-primary" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-primary text-lg">Minibar gratuito</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://pay.syshotelonline.it/reserva/sc_scheda.php?catena=8&hotel=97&lingua=I&stile=aiellosuite.css" target="_blank" class="bg-secondary text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-secondary transition-all duration-200 uppercase text-lg md:text-xl py-3 px-5 rounded-md flex flex-row items-center gap-2 group w-fit">
      Verifica Disponibilità
      <ChevronRight className="w-0 -translate-x-2 opacity-0 group-hover:translate-x-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:w-5 h-5 transition-all duration-200" />
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .bg-hero {
    @apply bg-cover bg-no-repeat relative;
		background-image: linear-gradient(180deg, #063661 0%,rgba(43,78,136,0.67) 54%), url("https://www.aiellohotels.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Milano-home.png");
    background-position: 50%;
	}

  .pattern {
    @apply absolute mt-auto w-full bottom-0 h-[100px] bg-no-repeat bg-cover z-[1] scale-y-[-1] scale-x-[1];
    background-size: 100% 100px;
    background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
  }
</style>